	  xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://apps.nextcloud.com/schema/apps/info.xsd">
	<id>files_confidential</id>
	<name>Confidential files</name>
	<summary>Workflows for handling confidential files in Nextcloud</summary>
	<description><![CDATA[
This app allows you to define a set of classification rules that will assign tags files.
For each classification rule you can define when the tag will be assigned to a file, based on text
content, BAILS classification metadata or Microsoft Information Purview metadata.
]]></description>
